      "bookmarkId": "924389_28_7136-7161",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "7136-7161",
      "markText": "妻子不动声色地回答说，把我也带走吧，我刚刚失明了。",
      "totalCount": 8228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7136&rangeEnd=7161",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=7136&rangeEnd=7161"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_26_10221-10236",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "10221-10236",
      "markText": "那天夜里，盲人梦见自己失明了。",
      "totalCount": 5280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=10221&rangeEnd=10236",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=10221&rangeEnd=10236"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_42_12705-12743",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "12705-12743",
      "markText": "我想我们没有失明，我想我们本来是盲人；能看得见的盲人；能看但又看不见的盲人。",
      "totalCount": 5280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=12705&rangeEnd=12743",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=12705&rangeEnd=12743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_25_527-583",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "527-583",
      "markText": "如果你能看，就要看见， 如果你能看见，就要仔细观察。",
      "totalCount": 4968,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=527&rangeEnd=583",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=527&rangeEnd=583"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_42_12811-12863",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "12811-12863",
      "markText": "然后她抬起头望望天空，看见天空一片白色。现在轮到我了，她想。突如其来的恐惧吓得她垂下眼帘。城市还在那里。",
      "totalCount": 4644,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=12811&rangeEnd=12863",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=12811&rangeEnd=12863"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_30_12605-12679",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "12605-12679",
      "markText": "这时，慢慢地，在两根竖着的铁栏杆之间出现了一张幽灵似的惨白的脸。是盲人的脸。士兵吓得血液都凝固了，正是由于害怕，他举枪瞄准，对着那幽灵射出一排子弹。",
      "totalCount": 4260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=12605&rangeEnd=12679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=12605&rangeEnd=12679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_37_6454-6535",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "6454-6535",
      "markText": "一个男人说，我觉得，要是不杀死他们的头目，我们不至于落到这般地步，如果像过去一样，女人们每月到那里去两次，满足一下他们本能的要求，我倒要问一声，这有什么了不起呢。",
      "totalCount": 4122,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=6454&rangeEnd=6535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=6454&rangeEnd=6535"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_27_1747-1841",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "1747-1841",
      "markText": "随着时代的推移，社会的进化和基因的置换，我们最后把道德感与血液的颜色和眼泪的咸淡混为一谈，仿佛这还不够，我们还把眼睛变成了朝向灵魂的镜子，结果它往往毫无保留地展示出我们嘴上试图否认的东西。",
      "totalCount": 2970,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=1747&rangeEnd=1841",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=1747&rangeEnd=1841"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_36_15587-15650",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "15587-15650",
      "markText": "七个女人都赤条条的，失眠的女人躺在床上，她一辈子也没有像现在这样干净过，另一个女人在一个接一个地为女伴们洗澡，最后又给自己洗。",
      "totalCount": 2702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=15587&rangeEnd=15650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=15587&rangeEnd=15650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_37_19048-19067",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "19048-19067",
      "markText": "大门一扇扇敞开了，疯子们跑出精神病院。",
      "totalCount": 2563,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=19048&rangeEnd=19067",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=19048&rangeEnd=19067"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_39_13775-13844",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "13775-13844",
      "markText": "她有生以来头一次问自己，是不是还有理由继续活下去。没有答案，答案在最需要的时候总是不肯出现，而很多时候唯一可能的答案却是，你必须耐心等待。",
      "totalCount": 2556,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=13775&rangeEnd=13844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=13775&rangeEnd=13844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_37_2821-2914",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "2821-2914",
      "markText": "我让你快活不成，医生的妻子想，胳膊随后猛地落下去。剪刀全力扎进盲人的咽喉，接着以自己为轴一转，割破了软骨和膜状组织，然后疯狂地扎得更深，直到碰到颈椎骨才不得不停下来。几乎没有听到他的喊声",
      "totalCount": 2541,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=2821&rangeEnd=2914",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=2821&rangeEnd=2914"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_29_6791-6811",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "6791-6811",
      "markText": "在一场瘟疫中不会有肇事者，我们都是受害者",
      "totalCount": 2505,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=924389&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=6791&rangeEnd=6811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94c325d05e1ae594c7c1535?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=6791&rangeEnd=6811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "924389_29_2181-2272",
